contents.page: # xxEROX The default prefix is **;** Use **;info** to get help. --- - Information: - help: ``displays help for the bot.`` - info: ``displays help for the bot.`` - changelog: ``displays the changelog.`` - servers: ``displays all commands.`` - userinfo: ``shows information about the respective account.`` - serverinfo: ``displays information about the respective server.`` - uptime: ``Displays the online time from the bot.`` --- - Staff-Members: - @xxAROX ➤ Head-Developer - @Stimorino ➤ Developer --- - Ads: - - [Website](http://enerybot.tk/xxerox/) - [GitHub](https://github.com/Aromastoffe/) - [YouTube](https://youtube.com/c/Aromastoffe/) - [Support](https://discordapp.com/invite/XwuyVAR)
